{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"40-listen-to-my-body","title":"Listen to My Body","description":"Each of us has a wonderful body. But have you ever listened to what it tells you?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Rohini Nilekani"],"illustrators":["Angie & Upesh"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/40-listen-to-my-body"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/700895/size3/19ca6ebcfc082bc86d63cf3227d13b74.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/700895/size6/19ca6ebcfc082bc86d63cf3227d13b74.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/427/size6/d69a115f0c159ea882793ba2cb41ff0a.jpg","text":"Today I am not going to school.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/428/size6/e67202d3c0724d1ae12f5525d9dc8856.jpg","text":"It is a holiday!","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/429/size6/50b694506f146bcdb0646ca8053f7a51.jpg","text":"Today I am not going to watch TV.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/430/size6/b8e641dba09c099282edc58af00491cf.jpg","text":"There is no electricity anyway.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/431/size6/3ecaea9bd358488c9ade06643ca1ecd5.jpg","text":"What am I going to do?","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/432/size6/f3770f7efffc083fda79a2a9dfc12dc7.jpg","text":"Today I am going to listen to my body!","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/433/size6/afb864fb23f4c5a4b37f085b77998e93.jpg","text":"First, I have to be quiet. Very quiet.\nSo that I can listen to my own body.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/434/size6/fd74e5e6b88ab5328e4dc167ed19caa1.jpg","text":"Yes, now I can hear my breath.\nIn... out... in... out...","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/435/size6/1c9e720d459b3ccf8cb58a0005633f99.jpg","text":"And I can make my breath noisier... Ssssssssssssss!\nAnd softer... Mmmmmmm.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/436/size6/e44035c6ff05d3c34ed2a3cb85a199f6.jpg","text":"And now I can hear my heart beating!\nDoodom, doodoom, dooodooom.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/437/size6/b33e0cc792cac701dd5bee3c6516c8d8.jpg","text":"Can I make my heart go faster or louder?\nYes, by jumping up and down twenty times.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/438/size6/1bbe179bec0c1fbc347d9ab5d699b2c7.jpg","text":"Now see, my heart is beating faster.\nDoodom, doodoom, dooodooom!","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/439/size6/02ba00623563facb600ff79966b52b87.jpg","text":"And if I put my fingers on my wrist\nthen I can hear my pulse!","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/440/size6/1443c997d29cf44512d1146a698cd5be.jpg","text":"And I can hear myself laughing\nHaha haha haaah haaa!","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/441/size6/275fab1b0e972aa9d8056ed203866692.jpg","text":"And crying\nBoohooohooo!","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/442/size6/65228cb2933cbaa00789deb9a4b0bb16.jpg","text":"And clapping\nTap tappa tap tapaa.","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/443/size6/e71f8fe4b9679488059ae940be347ec3.jpg","text":"And most of all - I can hear my stomach rumbling\nGuddu guddu guddu...","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/444/size6/1274d06379e74a021d185815759b20e2.jpg","text":"And saying\nFeed me, feed me.","words":null},{"n":19,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/445/size6/c8917f7ecb0112d31da482d8d6c9795f.jpg","text":"And my nose can hear jalebis frying in mothers kitchen.","words":null},{"n":20,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/446/size6/f8cd7c097e22a9bbb628b475b65ba8cc.jpg","text":"It is fun listening to my body.\nAnd now I want to hear my jaws chewing.","words":null},{"n":21,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/447/size6/ece2e176e7eccf901f54a55093b6bf30.jpg","text":"And my stomach slurping on mothers wonderful hot jalebis!","words":null},{"n":22,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/448/size6/da1518e56b316dfee44438575a9db48d.jpg","text":"Match  the  sounds  with \nthe  part  of  the  body\n \nHands                            Whistle\n \n \n \n \nLips                               Clap-clap\n \n \n \n \n \nFeet                              Stomp-stomp","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":22,"words":220}}